overview: Vivian and the gang are back home to celebrate her friend’s 18th birthday, and they won't let the birthday girl’s brother Xander spoil their fun.  Danny stumbles into the bathroom, catching Alessandra half-naked. She figures if he's going to be such a creeper, why not give him exactly what he wants?  Quinn was supposed to meet a man for a hot, sexy hookup during a work trip a year ago. Things went sour and they never ended up meeting. And then one night…he shows up to claim the hot fuck they both missed out on.  Karlee is spending her first time away from home on vacation in California, and her father’s friend Johnny has offered her a place to stay.  Violet’s blind date Keiran is a total dud who spoils the ending of her show's finale! What better way to silence a guy than sitting on his face?  Sophia is sick and tired of her annoying landlord Johnny pestering her for rent money, so she slips off her clothes and tells him to go to town or get out of her place.
title: Baby Got Boobs 18
